\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall ensure information systems implement the technical boundary protection,
 transmission,
 at-rest,
 cryptographic key management,
 and name-resolution controls required by this policy.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall maintain the cryptographic infrastructure required to satisfy this policy.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall implement compensating controls for approved exceptions to this policy.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Network Administrator:
