\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall configure boundary protection devices to enforce the Deny-by-Default traffic policy.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall maintain boundary protection devices in conformance with the Deny-by-Default traffic policy.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall implement network segregation between public,
 internal,
 and CJI-dedicated network segments.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall verify the integrity of network segregation through periodic configuration review.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall review firewall rule sets monthly to ensure no unauthorized access points exist.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Systems Administrator:
